reviews.title: Best
reviews.comment: The best profiler on Market: feature rich, customizable and getting better!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Almost perfect
reviews.comment: I\'ve tried them all, and this one seems to be working best on Jelly Bean (unlike some, who turned buggy after upgrading Android). Why not 5 stars? The icons are quite childish. More icons (especially monochrome and modern) would be highly appreciated.
reviews.author: tomer karni

reviews.title: Seems buggy
reviews.comment: The interface is nice and it is very customizable, but my location profiles aren\'t updating properly. Sometimes they\'ll work, and sometimes they won\'t. My work profile will change to home while I\'m at work. I think the location tracking function needs to be updated. Once this works consistently, it\'ll be a five star app. SGSIII
reviews.author: Ricardo Tucker

reviews.title: Makes my life so much easier!
reviews.comment: Switching profiles is so much easier with this app! I never have to think again about which profile I need to be switched on. Keep it up!
reviews.author: Rocky Pardjo

reviews.title: Needs WIFI only location detection
reviews.comment: I would like to see implemented a wifi only detection system for location. Not GPS, not cells, just wifi.  Everyone has wifi at work and if it could detect the wifi and enable a profile and when you leave it acted as leaving the profile then you would have the best app out there by far.  Please look into this.
reviews.author: Jason McArthur

reviews.title: Location Problems
reviews.comment: I really like this app, its easy to use and customize.  The main issue is the location switching, sometimes it works, sometimes not.  Currently I\'m at home, maps picks me up as being home, even the set location screen in the app sees my location, yet the app still says I\'m at work.  Needs fixing along with the schedule by calendar and then will be a great app.
reviews.author: Dave Stears

reviews.title: No silent mode
reviews.comment: Multiple simultaneous rules would be a nice addition. The location rules sometimes mix up (eg. showing \"Home\" at work). NFC not working with all tags. Can\'t be set up totally silent, always has either some sound or vibration or both.
reviews.author: Lari Perasto

reviews.title: Really like the cell location
reviews.comment: I really like this version because the cell tower location detection. It knows to change correct profile based on my location without using the GPS.
reviews.author: Roy Trieu

reviews.title: Outstanding
reviews.comment: Very customizable and user friendly, please keep up the great work, dev...
reviews.author: Lawrence L. Uhl Jr.

reviews.title: Very functional indeed
reviews.comment: If you got the patience to try different settings and their combinations,  this will be your optimal profile switch app.  It turns on my wifi when I\'m home,  turns on bluetooth and connects when I\'m in the car,  turns on silent profile when I\'m at work or in church. In other places,  my phone is on regular sound profile but with mobile data only.  Again, be patient to set up the rules and profile preferences.  It uses the network cells/gps and allows you determine the sensitivity around their use.
reviews.author: Achile Ali

reviews.title: Perfekt gestaltet. Aber Funktion misserabel
reviews.comment: 6 Sterne sobald wieder alles geht. Profilsteuerung \303\274ber Zeit, Ortsteuerung. Kann Anwendungen automatisch starten/beenden. Was mir noch fehlt ist das man mehrere Anwendungen zusammen ausw\303\244hlen kann. Negativ. Regeln \303\274ber Sendemast funktionieren nur sehr selten. dann w\303\244re es perfekt.
reviews.author: David Wolf

reviews.title: Good interface, but has some issues
reviews.comment: Sometimes it confusing my location: even if cells show HOME, it keep office profile, doesn\'t switching to the location. Today it switched to soundless night mode at the middle of the day, so the important calls missed!  And absolutely silently support: no reply to my two reports and no fix. So, sending messages to email useless.

reviews.title: Clever, flexible, saves menu access and battery
reviews.comment: This is the settings / profiles / power saving application I\'ve been looking for and hoped someone would write. Saves menu access to multiple settings by grouping into profiles. Quick choice and display of profile via 1x1 widget (no clutter). Allows auto selection of profile by rules based on location (cell proximity and/or GPS as preferred), time, calendar events, battery levels, wifi, etc. Very clever and polished. Definitely worth the small purchase price and the time to configure.
reviews.author: James Lees

reviews.title: Very useful
reviews.comment: An essential feature that was missing in Samsung\'s Firmware. Web stream is now possible without the phone going to sleep. Toggles are now rarely used by me.
reviews.author: Amado Liveira

reviews.title: Buggy - and thats a shame!
reviews.comment: Cant get this to work reliably on Nexus 4. * Calendar triggers fire for no reason * Doesn\'t work properly with multiple Bluetooth devices Developer does not respond to email. All a shame, because it could be a fantastic app for me :-(
reviews.author: Tony Armitstead

reviews.title: Perfect!
reviews.comment: Have rules set for my schedule. Rarely have to adjust my phone now. It\'s all automatic! No more forgetting to silence my phone in classes.
reviews.author: Matt Wiedemeier

reviews.title: Overall OK
reviews.comment: It is fine overall, except taht it will not turn off my network data. Try to use \"Mobile data network\" - turn off or \"Mobile network (APN) separately. So, I have to manually turn off network data.
reviews.author: Mihai Rainer

reviews.title: Near Perfect!
reviews.comment: It changes volume and power settings based on location, charging status, and battery level. Profiles can also be switched manually and temporarily.
reviews.author: Matthew van Voorthuijsen

reviews.title: Excellent Program
reviews.comment: I\'ve been using this for more than a year and it hasn\'t let me down. I love that it turns the WiFi on and off automatically so I never (rarely) have to do it myself.
reviews.author: Clifton Foster

reviews.title: AWESOME!
reviews.comment: I\'ve been an avid daily user for a long time! This app has always worked well for me. I can change a lot if things at the click of a widget and I can\'t tell you how valuable it is to me. Give it a chance, I assure you that you will like it!
reviews.author: A Google User
